com.amazon.clouddrive.model

Class DownloadFileRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazon.clouddrive.model.DownloadFileRequest
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CloudDriveRequest, java.lang.Comparable<CloudDriveRequest>

    public class DownloadFileRequest
extends java.lang.Object
implements CloudDriveRequest
    Defines the parameters of a request to Amazon Cloud Drive for downloading. The only required field to be set prior to passing this request to the AmazonCloudDrive is nodeId. The nodeId is the id of what should be downloaded. The optional member, viewBox, holds the requested size representing the longest edge of an item to be returned (i.e. the width of a landscape photo or video).
